0210   02 DTFORM      (A1)       /* Date format
0220   02 ERROR-TA    (A8)       /* Name of current error transaction
0230   02 STEPLIB     (A8)       /* Name of current steplib
0240   02 LANG-CODE   (I1)       /* Current language code
